多活8小时年轻时间<br/>我明天还要起来看贵金属大逃杀呢", "lou": 545, "content_length": 82, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 856332195, "postdatetimestamp": 1769700578}, {"pid": 856332614, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 27, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-29 23:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "早上追贵金属有色的不懂今晚能不能睡着了", "lou": 546, "content_length": 38, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1769700736}, {"pid": 856332894, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 29, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-29 23:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "[E1769700947 0 0]\t", "content": "[quote][pid=856332787,45974302,926]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66913250]未来呐[/uid] (2026-01-29 23:34):[/b]<br/><br/>没所谓啊，挂树上套一段时间呗，接着奏乐接着舞，明天搞原油接着套[s:ac:瞎][/quote]<br/><br/>明天至少油能活着出去 我感觉贵金属短期活不了  <br/>我说的是股票不是期货", "lou": 547, "content_length": 67, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 856332787, "postdatetimestamp": 1769700915}, {"pid": 856333124, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-29 23:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856332938,45974302,926]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66239373]zxcvbnmnga0[/uid] (2026-01-29 23:35):[/b]<br/><br/>石油王，你的黄金期货没动作吗[/quote]<br/><br/>我动他干啥 我剩下的单子3000多块的…这要一卖我根本买不回来<br/>我前面减过了", "lou": 548, "content_length": 73, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 856332938, "postdatetimestamp": 1769701065}, {"pid": 856333768, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 101, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-29 23:44", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我只能说我跑的时候能招呼一声就不错了，有时候没办法解释，毕竟没有出现问题之前大部分人只会想 为什么这个人那么蠢有钱都不想挣[s:ac:闪光]", "lou": 549, "content_length": 118, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1769701492}, {"pid": 856334700, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-29 23:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856334525,45974302,928]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=33490717]阿斯达斯d[/uid] (2026-01-29 23:52):[/b]<br/><br/>油算是第3天？昨天想起来大宗的传递路线，今天进了油和化工，不会现在大宗传的这么快吧，贵金属刚结束油也要结束了？[/quote]<br/><br/>又要能死我今天就是清仓了，放心至少期货那边死不到哪里去，不过股票套利太严重，有时候情绪杀这种没办法，减仓了有盈利才能持仓", "lou": 550, "content_length": 125, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 856334525, "postdatetimestamp": 1769702063}, {"pid": 856351117, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 08:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856337583,45974302,930]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39803674]green hat[/uid] (2026-01-30 00:29):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大不做期货铜了吗，之前说避险，现在应该风险过去了吧[/quote]<br/>说完那三天不是释放了么，都什么时候的事了。现在铜油都会补涨。只是我做了原油  就没做铜了<br/>钱没那么多 而且期货不宜分散开超市  真的会死。", "lou": 551, "content_length": 131, "reply_to": 856337583, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769731973}, {"pid": 856351656, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 41, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 08:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856351516,45974302,932]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-01-30 08:18):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大说他昨天-4， 雨神也说了昨天-4。这么一看我-5好像也不是那么不可接受[s:ac:呆]  昨天科技人都吃了大面[/quote]<br/>我是科技ETF-4 不是我持仓-4", "lou": 552, "content_length": 30, "reply_to": 856351516, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769732380}, {"pid": 856351986, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 52, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 08:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856351710,45974302,932]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-01-30 08:20):[/b]<br/><br/>我就是看他半夜还在盯期货，这么早又起来回复帖子估计还得早盘再看看各个指标贴水股指之类的。[/quote]<br/>年轻人不要睡那么多 70以后你天天睡不醒都行 你现在熬的是年轻的夜  用的是以后的时间，你刷过信用卡吗？一样的<br/>我还要看外围局势 比如最近就在看印尼金融市场，所以这次美元反弹那一根我没卖黄金就是因为我知道这次美元反弹是因为吃了一点印尼的肉，而且这种可能蔓延到泰国 马来西亚。<br/>如果看不懂就当我没说。", "lou": 553, "content_length": 285, "reply_to": 856351710, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769732635}, {"pid": 856362603, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 95, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 09:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "不要随便抄底", "lou": 554, "content_length": 12, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769738096}, {"pid": 856366824, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 55, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 10:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "跌破4100了  反抽之后如果上不了4126 我减仓到40%内", "lou": 555, "content_length": 45, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769739780}, {"pid": 856368837, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 10:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "恐慌盘出来了  等反抽再说", "lou": 556, "content_length": 22, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769740549}, {"pid": 856373171, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 133, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 11:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正你们记得 急跌 不割肉，等反弹不行 重新下跌再考虑割肉的事", "lou": 557, "content_length": 56, "14": {"14": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769742193}, {"pid": 856373384, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 11:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反弹回均线了 我减一点设备ETF", "lou": 558, "content_length": 27, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1769742275}, {"pid": 856374398, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-30 11:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=856374259,45974302,959]Reply[/pid] 